tourBios.carHigh: Finished T14 at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou. Tied with Chang Wei Wang, Yi Yuan Mi and Hao Chuan Wu, so the quartet had a playoff to determine the final two fully-exempt playing spots for the PGA TOUR China Series' season. Earned his card on the first extra hole when he made birdie to the other players' pars. Â

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was 109th in 2015 at the Yulongwan Yunnan Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T93rd in First Tee Late Par 5 Scoring A on the PGA Tour China Series.
